Part A. Install turtlebot on ros-melodic
Since there isn't an official support for turtlebot in melodic, please use the following link to installturtlebot manually into melodic: https://github.com/gaunthan/Turtlebot2-On-Melodic

In case it shows some problems below, please install extra packages:
1. gazebo plugin error: apt install ros-melodic-gazebo-ros-pkgs
2. depth_image_proc-Config error: sudo apt install ros-melodic-depth-image-proc

Part B. Run turtlebot
please guarantee executable command to the python file in wander_bot/scripts/wander_bot.py
All parameters are stored in wander_bot.launch file so you may adjust it yourself.
